OL,3,CTories call for independent pay body
OL,4,Cfor public sector rail workers
OL,6,FGovernment moves to help nationalise
OL,7,Ftrain operation should include
OL,8,Festablishing an independent pay review
OL,9,Fprocess for public sector rail
OL,10,Fworkers, according to the Tories.
OL,12,FShadow transport secretary Helen
OL,13,FWhately said the proposal would "take
OL,14,Fthe politics out of pay" and be in
OL,15,Fline with arrangements in place for
OL,16,Fteachers, nurses and the armed forces.
