OL,3,CTories call for independent pay body
OL,4,Cfor public sector rail workers
OL,6,FThe proposed amendment to the
OL,7,FPassenger Railway Services (Public
OL,8,FOwnership) Bill follows the new Labour
OL,9,FGovernment making a multi-year pay
OL,10,Foffer to train drivers in a bid to
OL,11,Fresolve long-running pay disputes and
OL,12,Fend strikes.
OL,14,FThe Bill is being fast-tracked through
OL,15,Fthe House of Commons and is expected
OL,16,Fto clear its remaining stages on
OL,17,FTuesday before the House of Lords
OL,18,Fexamines it.
