OL,3,CTories call for independent pay body
OL,4,Cfor public sector rail workers
OL,6,FIt would ensure that appointing a
OL,7,Fpublic sector train operator as
OL,8,Fexisting contracts expire becomes the
OL,9,Fdefault position rather than a last
OL,10,Fresort.
OL,12,FThis would mean privately-owned
OL,13,Foperators such as Avanti West Coast,
OL,14,FEast Midlands Railway, Great Western
OL,15,FRailway and Thameslink would be
OL,16,Fgradually brought into public
OL,17,Fownership.
