OL,3,CTories call for independent pay body
OL,4,Cfor public sector rail workers
OL,6,FMs Whately accused the Government of
OL,7,F"rushing these huge changes through"
OL,8,Fand treating the railways "like a toy
OL,9,Ftrain set".
OL,11,FThe Conservatives' amendments to be
OL,12,Fconsidered on Tuesday also include
OL,13,Frequiring annual reporting of the
OL,14,Fperformance of publicly-owned train
OL,15,Foperating companies and maintaining
OL,16,Fspace for private providers on the
OL,17,Fnetwork.
