OL,6,FPA news agency analysis shows nearly a
OL,7,Fquarter (23%) of rail journeys in
OL,8,FBritain are on services that are
OL,9,Falready publicly-owned.
OL,11,FMs Whately said: "Everyone agrees that
OL,12,Four rail system needs reform. But
OL,13,FLabour are rushing these huge changes
OL,14,Fthrough with none of the proper
OL,15,Fscrutiny. They're treating our railway
OL,16,Flike a toy train set.
