OL,3,CTories call for independent pay body
OL,4,Cfor public sector rail workers
OL,6,F"Putting politicians in charge of the
OL,7,Fcontrols isn't the magical solution
OL,8,Fthey think it is. It just means
OL,9,Fpassengers and taxpayers footing the
OL,10,Fbill when they lose their grip on
OL,11,Fcosts. That's why we're proposing
OL,12,Fchecks to hold ministers to account.
OL,14,F"Teachers, nurses, and our armed
OL,15,Fforces all have independent pay bodies
OL,16,Fto take the politics out of pay. If
OL,17,FLabour block one for rail unions it's
OL,18,Fpretty clear where their loyalties
OL,19,Flie. It'll be back to beer and
OL,20,Fsandwiches at Number 10."
